    "id": "e721",
    "subject": "English",
    "page": 57,
    "chapter": "Chapter 2\nChapter 2",
    "content": "43\nMridang\n— jumping over the canals! \n— climbing the trees!\n— swinging from the branches!\n— watching garden lizards!\nYet we reach school on time.\nA. What time do you leave home for school? At what time \ndoes your school start?\nB. Tell your classmates about the fun you had on your way \nto school.\nNew words\nschool | paddy | fields |"
