    "content": "17\nA. \u0007Look at the picture and observe different musical \ninstruments.\n \ni. \u0007Circle \n the musical instruments that are similar in \nshape to a \n drum.\n \nii. \u0007Tick ü the musical instruments that are similar in \nshape to a \n matka.\n \niii. \u0007Tick ü the shape similar to the shape of a \nshehnai ( \n, \n, \n ).\n \niv. \u0007How is the shape of harmonium"
