    "page": 39,
    "chapter": "Guess my Number",
    "content": "7, _______, _________, ________, _______\n40   45   50   55   60   65   70   75\nB. 40, 45, 50, _______, _________, ________, _______, _______\n50   60   70   80   90\nC. 50, 60, _______, _________, ________"
