    "chapter": "Let us Play — Bingo!",
    "content": "31\nLet us Play — Bingo!\nEncourage children to develop their strategy for selecting the \nnumbers to be written on the grid.\nMake a 3 × 4 grid \n for playing ‘Bingo’.\nFill the boxes of the grid with any number from 2 to 12. \nNumbers can be repeated.\nLet one child throw two dice and say the sum of the numbers \nof dots on the dice."
