    "content": "34\nA. Trace the shape of the objects around you. For example, \neraser, leaf, matchbox, sharpener, pencil colour, etc.\nB. Draw the shapes you get after tracing.\nLet us Think\nLet us Trace\nWrite the names of objects that have the same trace as:\nA. Bottle cap \n \n \nB. Eraser"
