    "chapter": "Hide and Seek",
    "content": "35\nHide and Seek\nCircle \n and rectangle \n are playing hide and seek. \nRectangle is hiding from the circle.\nWhere should\nI hide? Oh!\nShoe box\n1, 2, 3... 10\nI am coming.\nI look like the \nface of the shoe \nbox. I will hide \nbehind it.\nWhere are \nyou? Are you \nbehind the \nphoto frame?"
