    "chapter": "Hide and Seek",
    "content": "36\nWhere should \nI hide?\nThe door bell \nrang, Triangle \nand Square came \nand joined the \ngame.\nWhere are you? \nAre you behind \nthe TV?\nI caught you! You \nare behind the \nshoe box.\nIt is my turn \nnow 1, 2, 3...10"
