    "content": "39\nAsk children to explore various objects around them and ask \nthem to find out the number of their edges, corners and sides.\nOrigami Fun!\nA. \u0007Take a paper and fold it to make it a square.\nB. It has \n corners and \n edges.\nC. \u0007Fold it in half by joining two corners as \nshown in the picture.\nD. Tick ü the shape which you get."
