    "id": "m2933",
    "subject": "Maths",
    "page": 55,
    "chapter": "Let us Do",
    "content": "41\nNitya is playing with leaves and making patterns.\nNow you also collect some leaves and make a pattern. Paint \none side of the leaf and print it on the space given below.\nLet us Do\nProject Work\nMake a wall hanging using cutouts of different shapes with the help of \nyour elders to decorate your home or classroom."
