    "content": "A. Circle \n the aasanas with standing or vertical lines.\nB. Tick ü the aasanas with both vertical and slanting lines.\nC. Cross  the aasanas which have curved lines.\nD. Put a star  along the aasanas that have sleeping or \nhorizontal lines.\nE. Try some of these aasanas. Discuss the lines that you \nnotice while doing the aasanas."
