    "page": 82,
    "chapter": "Let us Do",
    "content": "\u0007There were 40 balloons\n and 13 balloons got \nburst. How many balloons are left? \nD. \n\u0007Kanika made 72 bangles \n. She sold 36 bangles. \nHow many bangles are left with Kanika now? \nE. \n\u000756 birds were sitting on the tree \n. A few more \nbirds joined them. Now there are 87 birds. Find out the \nnumber of birds that came later."
