    "id": "m3445",
    "subject": "Maths",
    "page": 84,
    "chapter": "Hania and Mansi’s Gift",
    "content": "apper is `24 \nand the cost of ribbons is `37. \nA. How much money did they spend? \nB. How much money is left with them? \n \nHere, 3 + 9 = 12 9 + 6 = 15\n6 + 5 = 11 5 + 3 = 8\nProject Work\nDaljeet has solved some questions and writen down their answers. \nWhat do you think? Are they correct? Verify the answers. \nCorrect it if you find them wrong."
