    "content": "92\nLet us make the table \nof 7 from the tables \nof 3 and 4.\nProject Work\nCollect 24 small objects like buttons, bottle caps, pebbles, etc. Arrange \nthem in different arrays and write the related multiplication facts. How \nmany of these facts can you find? Record your answers in the table given \nbelow.\nNumber of groups\nMultiplication facts"
