    "chapter": "Let us Discuss",
    "content": "99\nA. In which season do you go on a vacation?\nB. Your birthday falls in which season of the year?\nC. Which is your favourite season? Why?\nD. What is special about your favourite season?\nLeaves fall \non the ground. \nPleasant winds \non the way, \nis when it is an \nautumn day.\nWinter is when \nI’m all in snow\nfrom head to toe."
