    "content": "106\nA. \u0007Why did the family plan a trip? To which place did they \ngo for the trip? What did you like about their trip?\nB. \u0007On which day did they begin their journey? When did \nthey come back? How long was their trip?\nC. Which places did they visit in their trip? \nD. How long was their day trip in:\n \ni. Manglagiri hills _______ hours"
