    "content": "on in terms of days and hours. \nAlso discuss what is special about their cities.\n______ hours\n______ hours\nDo you know? \nVande Bharat is the fastest \ntrain in India. The train is \ndesigned in India only and \nis also India’s first train to \nhave an integrated engine \nand not a separate engine \ncoach.\nAmazing Fact"
