    "content": "136\nO. How many rectangles can be made after joining the \ndots given below?\nHint: Square is also a type of rectangle.\nP. Complete these by using addition or subtraction \nof numbers.\n18 – 9\n6 + 3\n9\n13\n19\nQ. A shepherd has 4 sheep and 4 dogs. Divide the garden \ninto 4 areas, such that each portion or area contains \none tree, one sheep and one dog."
